      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am a third-year master student in &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn&#34;&gt;Tsinghua University&lt;/a&gt;, under the supervision of Prof. Yuxing Han. I earned my bachelor&amp;rsquo;s degree from &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.bjtu.edu.cn&#34;&gt;Beijing Jiaotong University&lt;/a&gt; in 2023.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;My research interest focuses on &lt;strong&gt;Machine Learning&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Computer Vision&lt;/strong&gt;, especially &lt;strong&gt;Efficient AI&lt;/strong&gt; algorithms and systems. From 2021, I started my research on efficient physiological time series analysis based on knowledge distillation. Now, I focus on efficient video computer vision systems with video motion estimation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
